overview.zh: 参加VITE的矿业运行! 通过在钱包中持有SVB代币，您将立即有资格以0.02％（每年7.2％）的每日固定利息支付，每天以FAST支付1 SVB = 1 FAST。
overview.en: Participate in the VITE mining operation! By holding SVB tokens in your wallet, you are immediately eligible for a 0.02% fixed daily interest (7.2% annual), paid in VITE daily. 1 SVB = 1 VITE.
